{"id":3829,"title":"[Chemotherapy risk assessment for elderly patients].","abstract":"The incidence of cancer increases with age and most elderly patients will choose chemotherapy, and the complications of cytotoxic chemotherapy will be more common in these patients. Therefore, it is particularly important to predict the chemotherapy toxicity for the elderly patients. This review article summarizes the recent chemotherapy risk assessment tools for the elderly patients.","date":"2014-11-01","categories":"Neoplasms","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25360657","annotations":[{"name":"Old age","weight":0.338298,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Old_age"},{"name":"Risk","weight":0.267804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk"},{"name":"Risk assessment","weight":0.210212,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk_assessment"},{"name":"Chemotherapy","weight":0.169585,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemotherapy"},{"name":"Cancer","weight":0.151091,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer"},{"name":"Incidence (epidemiology)","weight":0.0585202,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Incidence_(epidemiology)"},{"name":"Prediction","weight":0.0532834,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prediction"},{"name":"Toxicity","weight":0.0494293,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toxicity"},{"name":"Cytotoxicity","weight":0.0294679,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cytotoxicity"},{"name":"Complication (medicine)","weight":0.0248395,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complication_(medicine)"},{"name":"Senior citizen","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Senior_citizen"},{"name":"Review article","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Review_article"},{"name":"Psychological evaluation","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psyc